---
import { PAINS } from '../consts'
import Icon from './Icon.astro'
---

<section class="mx-auto grid max-w-[1120px] gap-12 px-6 py-24 lg:grid-cols-[5fr_7fr] lg:gap-16">
  <!-- 左：标题列 -->
  <div class="reveal lg:pt-2">
    <span class="text-[13px] font-medium text-muted">为什么要做这套系统</span>
    <h2 class="mt-3 text-[2rem] leading-tight md:text-[2.25rem]">
      纸笔加 Excel 的考试，<br class="hidden sm:block" />把老师拖在重复劳动里
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-5 max-w-md text-[15px] leading-[1.8] text-body">
      下面五件事，几乎每个组织过考试的老师都遇到过。这套系统就是冲着它们去的。
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- 右：痛点列表（非卡片网格，纵向条目） -->
  <ul class="reveal divide-y divide-line border-y border-line">
    {
      PAINS.map((p) => (
        <li class="flex gap-4 py-5">
          <span class="mt-0.5 flex h-9 w-9 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-line text-muted">
            <Icon name={p.icon} class="h-[18px] w-[18px]" />
          </span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-[15px] font-semibold text-ink">{p.title}</h3>
            <p class="mt-1 text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-body">{p.text}</p>
          </div>
        </li>
      ))
    }
  </ul>
</section>
